1. Task Description
    https://adventofcode.com/2021/day/2

2. Summary:
    2.1 Day 2-1
        Starting at 0,0, calculate the product of the new coordinates after applying the movements input.

        forward:    + horizontal
        down:       + depth
        up:         - depth

3. Example:
    3.1 Day 2-1
        forward 5
        down    5
        forward 8
        up      3
        down    8
        forward 2

        Ans: 15 * 10 = 150


4. Run the program
    cd AoC_2021_Day_2
    make run

5. Run the tests
    cd AoC_2021_Day_2
    make test
